&lt;p&gt;Microsoft Exchange Server 2010&lt;br /&gt;
Microsoft Exchange Server 2013&lt;br /&gt;
Microsoft Exchange Server 2016&lt;br /&gt;
Microsoft Exchange Server 2019&lt;/p&gt;
